name: Chucho's Birth
description: The story starts when Einfelsen fulfilled the prophecy of raising the Last Dragon of the Fairy Realm, meaning the destruction of humanity. "The boys" of the Space realm came to kill all humans to destroy the last egg, but the scientist achieved to save Chucho before he and all his Race died. Now Chucho is the King of the Fairy realm and wants revenge so he started training to become the "strongest creature of the Universe".
